One last post.

::KitKat::
She looked at FOxFingers and Drillbit. "Keep Him here Drillbit. I 
have to go meet Megatron."
She walked out.   

She walked out to the entrance where she saw GoldenEye. "Glad to se 
that you made it. Go inside and get squared away.  I have business to 
take care of."

She walked out and towards the clearing. 
She opened her link. "Destructor, I'm off to meet with Megatron in 
the clearing. I shall see you when I get back."

She walked over and looked at the clearing through the trees. 
Megatron had another bot with him. Sighed and gathered all her 
strength.  She walked out and looked at Megatron.
"I am here. Now let's talk."
